{"type": "article", "id": 58372, "title": "Beyoncé 收购个人品牌 Ivy Park，以及，Elton John 出演 John Lewis 圣诞广告｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2018-11-16T05:05:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25746, "name": "Ivy Park"}, {"id": 46247, "name": "Birkenstock"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 331, "name": "John Lewis"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181116130235XQrfA4GF2Ysv69Sk.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/chinese-online-gen-z-expected-drive-luxury-goods-growth-in-1202908000/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2018 - 2025 年个人奢侈品市场增幅将维持在 3% - 5%</a></strong>｜贝恩咨询于周四发布年度奢侈品展望报告 Bain &amp; Co. Luxury Goods Worldwide Market Study，预计 2018 至 2025 年个人奢侈品销售额的增幅将维持在 3% 至 5%，到 2025 年全球总销售额将达到 3200 亿至 3650 亿欧元之间。</p><p>其它重要数据还包括：中国消费者所贡献的市场份额将从 32% 上升至 45%；线上销售额占比将从 10% 增至 25%；新开店铺数量将减少，实体店的作用主要转变为消费者触点；Z 世代和千禧一代将贡献 55% 的购买；品牌的跨界融合更加突出，从时尚、生活方式到运动。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/beyonce-buys-out-ivy-park-brand-from-philip-green\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beyoncé 收购与 Topshop 创始人合作创立的个人品牌 Ivy Park</a></strong>｜Beyoncé 于两年前与 Topshop 创始人 Philip Green 合作创立了个人品牌 Ivy Park，并拥有该品牌 50% 的股权。根据《金融时报》及 BoF 报道，Beyoncé Knowles 计划在几周后完成对 Ivy Park 的收购，但未透露具体金额等细节。交易完成后，该品牌将继续在 Topshop 内发售。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/sneaker/373388/032c-x-birkenstock-lianmingxielvxiliezaoxing-lookbook-fabu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BIRKENSTOCK x 032c 推出联名鞋履系列。</a></strong><br></p><p>032 是总部位于柏林的一个杂志兼服饰品牌。该系列在 BIRKENSTOCK Super Birki 木鞋款型的基础上做了改造，Lookbook 由 Christian Werner 掌镜，模特分别是 032c 时尚总监 Marc Goehring 与 Nunguja Kisalya，将自 11 月 22 日起发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110740aGHBTX9RwVFbci2m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811161107400ZKJc7qrRzI4bBlg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110739U9P2zYsvXw6paldh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110737rvOgNwKLjHa2FM37.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110739714wALrXEeJ3Sutm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110737j8nNbDiy6u7wUaWH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110738nkuhL2qxAQFoPsbr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110734NM36Obs4CHyULTqV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110735PX3Isxz810YdW7vl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110735sRvlIrbX9x6GZDj1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110736fJGRLEn6d3HlorYU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116110737W0PwhM4aQBIJuEyH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/11/alexander-wang-collection-1-drop-1-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang 发布品牌更新后的第一组广告大片。</a></strong><br></p><p>今年 6 月，Alexander Wang 发布了品牌更新后的第一场秀、公布了新 Logo 并且表示将从传统的走秀-买手模式转向类似潮牌的定期上架新品模式（drop）。在新系列 Collection 1 中，他强调从第一代华裔移民视角看待美国流行文化，塑造了牛仔、自行车手、运动员等一系列带有强烈美国风格的形象。</p><p>刚发布的大片延续了这种思路。你可以看到典型的高中拉拉队长、橄榄球运动员、选美女孩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112554brgNQfCy0xRcdZXh.png\" data-ratio=\"1.243292\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112553adsYEZLSvjRrHtIi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.247500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112549Q7xnpBP1cmo9X0y5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.247500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112553GFwRprYlucjBX8ig.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.651250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112555BcZQaRjsvXe7zUh1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.651250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112555f4B20ztREHZ7NkIP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.651250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116112552PotN4aQxsmdlAq85.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.651250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/11/new-york-department-store-holiday-windows-displays-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">临近圣诞节，纽约各大百货公司和品牌旗舰店开始布置华丽的橱窗。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113050wZJUYdfj2sbk1m0Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.592500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Tiffany &amp; Co.</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113050f8pBhlyTksmdbJ1P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.598000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113052KBjmZDkFcu9zGORr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.567000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811161130533LZc4bRlSvBTumkg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.589000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113053sw8tcgnopKldF3Ue.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.626500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811161131361EfL5JDpoFyGgcX4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.677500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Louis Vuitton</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113156FmSJn6PExaI5tpKB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.644000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113222R4WZxTIkzUbG0cSB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Barneys New York</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113222u0YaSUFZ7lvcgOmB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811161132233eZkUy4JCc8Kj92i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113224uQIjspVNhSRDYqHU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.351351\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113305R90OHqefNpCmuKnW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Bloomingdale's&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113306bvmOtu3gl29GpJNh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113303xrqPhJnRa1d3yV0K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.922000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113306cmdxBlNoeCK0TZOQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116113307giurEaFLlK1fOD8Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018111611330820GXtIm6oWRKnHMN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/the-boy-and-the-piano-john-lewis-christmas-advert-2018-review-elton-john-your-song-a8633881.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elton John 出演 John Lewis 圣诞广告</a></strong>，唱的是他 17 岁时和老朋友 Bernie Taupin 花 10 分钟共同创作的第一支热门单曲“Your Song”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116115802YTc3sOoxMQGVWP89.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562155\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116115805Ky9HWAL8pfgP7vrw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562155\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116115806EdAYGIObfUHsLqSC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562155\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116115806OMw81QPpBFXoGsAW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562155\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116115807YSUqrCgNyTGMxQEt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562155\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e07939a0crf\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"http://purple.fr/magazine/los-angeles-issue-30/best-of-women/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purple Magazine&nbsp;拍摄的洛杉矶造型特辑“Best of Women”。</a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116121241wd4ApY9RB2gjPU1V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.267327\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116121242iUc4g0uW2XrJ5Dd8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.299492\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181116121242ZJBcmVIl38Qyus9F.jpg\" data-ratio=